Name: assign_worker_to_task
Description: Assignment of a worker to a specific task

Name: task_effort_estimate
Description: Estimated effort for a task in hours

Name: sprint_duration_days
Description: Number of days in a sprint

Name: story_points_estimate
Description: Story points assigned to a User Story

Name: worker_availability_fraction
Description: Percentage of time a worker is available for sprint

Name: number_of_sprints_in_release
Description: Total sprints planned for a release

Name: feature_priority_rank
Description: Priority rank of a feature in backlog

Name: planned_release_date
Description: Target date for feature release (as Unix timestamp)

Name: team_size_count
Description: Number of members in a Scrum team

Name: documentation_status_flag
Description: Indicates if feature documentation is complete

Name: moderation_assignment
Description: Scrum Master assigned to moderate event

Name: goal_achievement_score
Description: Score indicating degree of Sprint Goal achievement

Name: feedback_rating
Description: Sprint Review feedback rating from stakeholders
